**Back-reference**: `x-issue-start 00009` â†’ `.scaffoldx/xissues/active/0001-0300/ISS_00009_rms_window_mismatch.md`
**Related Task**: Task 0003 (Mic Test Screen)
**Code Location**: `AudioAnalyzer.java:81` | `SettingsForm.java:1087`

**What was done**:

- Standardized all RMS analysis to 100ms windows (matching SilenceRemover)
- AudioAnalyzer.java: Changed from 20ms to 100ms windows
